title: Did Pelosi Stage Photo of Herself Getting COVID-19 Vaccine?
subtitle: Members of Congress were among the first people in the U.S. to receive the vaccine in 2020.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: Photographs that circulated in mid-December 2020 showed U.S. House Speaker Nancy Pelosi, a Democrat from California, receiving her COVID-19 vaccination with a needle that was still sealed with its orange cap.
